column4: "Assist in the marketing of events & helps set up/take down for events."

"Advance personal development through community service, philanthropic fundraising, & activities."

"The purpose of the Club is to share in camaraderie through tabletop board games (and other activities of a similar genre), and to build a community of friendship and understanding across all social boundaries. "
"he mission of the USUSA Paintball Club is to offer all USU students the opportunity to learn, experience, and engage in paint-balling in a fun and safe environment."
"Come and play table tennis if you want to have fun with it!"
"The purpose of USUSA Spikeball Roundnet Club is to provide an opportunity for students of Utah State University to learn and play the sport of Spikeball in a friendly and competitive environment."
